1. *Cao*! (Hello!)
2. Zdravo, *cao* svima! (Hi, hello everyone!)
3. Svi smo se već pozdravili, *cao*! (We've all said hello already, bye!)
4. Ona je samo kratko rekla *cao* i otišla. (She just said bye and left.)
5. Sećam se da je ona uvek bila jako ljubazna i završavala razgovor sa *cao*! (I remember she was always very kind and ended the conversation with bye!)